<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1167091-is-this-book-part-of-a-series-or-can-i">Is this book part of a series or can I read just this book and not the ones before it and still understand whats going on?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1167091'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F31371230-house-of-spies">like</a></span>

