<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1162259-nearing-the-end-of-house-of-spies-and-have">Nearing the end of House of Spies and have a question. In Chapter 60, Keller, Mikhail, Natalie and Olivia begin walking &quot;due west into a sea of sand&quot;. Then, in Chapter 61 they are driving with Dina and Eli in a Nissan and a Jeep. How did they meet up? It&#39;s not relevant to the story but I was curious. Another great book by Daniel Silva.</a>
