<span id="freeTextContainer2713614385886203924">Typical Silva/Allon thriller. Procedural as Allon and his merry band follow the leads via trickery and interrogation chase a head of a terrorist organization. A continuation of Black Widow.<br/><br/>Nothing really special here. A well worn Silva/Allon formula. As novels go, Silva has done better work with the Allon character.</span>

